        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-cell">
            <div class="stat-num">10</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Programs tested</div>
            <div class="stat-delta">Across all 4 categories</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-cell">
            <div class="stat-num">90</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Day window</div>
            <div class="stat-delta">Mar–May 2026</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-cell">
            <div class="stat-num">90</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Live clients</div>
            <div class="stat-delta">Across 3 agency books</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-cell">
            <div class="stat-num">$5.2K</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Total spend</div>
            <div class="stat-delta">On reseller partners</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta dark">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want the reseller margin benchmark?</h4>
            <p>Margin per retainer, time-to-deliverable, retention, per partner — segmented by book size. <strong>Free CSV, no follow-up.</strong></p>
